# ===========================================
# SpeakRight Environment Variables
# Desktop app — service keys are configured in-app
# This file is kept for reference only
# ===========================================

# No server-side environment variables needed.
# API keys are configured in the Settings page and stored locally on the user's
# machine. The desktop build uses the OS credential store where supported.
#
# Do not put real API keys, tokens, recordings, or exported user data in this
# file or in Git.
